Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 歡迎歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出迎場面很大 方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.90,0:02:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 志志雄 志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.08,0:02:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十九話\N製造逆刃刀的人\N新井赤空最後的一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一回到京都就覺得很安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 往這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新至今十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.46,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在日本全國四處遊走\N唯有這個地方沒有再來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.67,0:02:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末期的動亂\N沒有一天不充滿血腥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.41,0:02:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彷彿地獄圖畫般打鬥的戰場\N就在這京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.51,0:02:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發什麼呆啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看！到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵屋餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餐廳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 在京都小有名氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂？小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比以前回來得遲些  害我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 因為發生許多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛…痛死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來晚了處罰你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐 歡迎歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長高了 長高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.36,0:03:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒謝謝你 休息一下再走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.26,0:03:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是緋村拔刀齊 ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算十字刀疤隱藏起來\N知道的人還是知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到裏面再詳談 請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先去洗個澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.22,0:04:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在道上沒說自己是\N「隱密御庭番眾」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.87,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柏崎念至以前是\N御庭番眾成員之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名為京都探索員「阿翁」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.04,0:04:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開這間葵屋是做為京都聚點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.48,0:04:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江戶幕府總店先倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過維新後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.68,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就變成那些沒事做的同志\N他們暫時的落腳處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還滿有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以蒼紫才把小操寄在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識蒼紫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.80,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該先跟你說才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣\N般若們死了而蒼紫行蹤不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.14,0:05:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你暫時要對小操保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.72,0:05:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村你十年不曾出現在京都\N現在來難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.82,0:05:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你的接班人\N志志雄真實有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.30,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我鍛練有素\N京都內外的事我大概都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耳中傳入他在京都造反之事\N我簡直不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.01,0:05:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你也現身了我不得不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.31,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好不好？\N我強力的支持你做你後盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.85,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡現在的京都\N有人要破壞的話絕不饒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護京都\N老兵要再度出征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下 啊啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這間葵屋沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家以前都是隱密御庭番眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.81,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起保護小操\N都是可信任的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不要也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是養大小操的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說了你也不聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就我不客氣拜託你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想請你幫我找人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新井赤空和比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡可能快點找到這兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起床了緋村 天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經起來了啊\N本想看看你睡眼惺忪的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啦…小操 你穿那樣是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是京都的家居服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼說穿著忍者服\N在老家走來走去有點那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿翁 這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿翁老先生早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要找的人裏面\N其中一個有消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 正確的說\N應該是知道他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.21,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製造逆刃刀的刀匠\N新井赤空在八年前已經作古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.45,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀匠…對了\N要打一把替代折斷的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.12,0:07:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那位刀匠已經死了\N就不會有第二把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.56,0:07:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過還有希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.06,0:07:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空把所有的技術\N傳給他兒子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要現在就去看看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我白天出去會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.44,0:07:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手是志志雄\N你怎麼躲藏終究會被發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.71,0:07:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿翁老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村你不是為了本國的人民\N而和志志雄戰鬥的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.45,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以正大光明的去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是正直男人的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？說得不錯吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看爺爺這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.76,0:08:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前還被推舉為\N隱密御庭番眾最有力接班人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他說\N今後是年輕人活躍的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.44,0:08:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推薦蒼紫做接班人\N自已反倒屈居做京都探索員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新井赤空\N幕府末期有名的刀匠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.18,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,致力於探究斬人刀、殺人刀等\N被刀匠界視為異類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.56,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,探究殺人刀的刀匠\N製造出不殺人的逆刃刀來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.60,0:08:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人的人生\N有時會讓人覺得矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對？緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.54,0:08:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空的兒子新井青空\N繼承擔任刀匠的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在是明治時代\N刀劍不受重視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.41,0:09:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前以是打制菜刀\N鐮刀等的生活用具維生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定\N他可以製造出新的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問新井青空在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啦…青空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在 窩搜 窩搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？窩搜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,窩搜 窩搜 窩搜 窩搜\N不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手\N窩搜 窩搜 窩搜 窩搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要握手啊 好乖好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.07,0:09:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織 不可以頑皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨 需要什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想買一把菜刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以試切看看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…  又黏起來 回復原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,復原刀法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次見到\N切口組織完全沒有破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切下去又回復原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.91,0:10:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名刀結合高手的技術\N是高難度的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單的菜刀就能做到\N不愧是赤空的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太厲害了 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.59,0:10:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的逆刃刀\N就決定給新井青空製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.02,0:10:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆娘 可以讓我見青空嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要請青空打造一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公  爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們好 我是新井青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是青空？怎麼不太像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那邊去再聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.82,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於一定要我來打刀一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我已經不打刀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們去找別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.33,0:11:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知道家父赤空\N探究殺人刀一事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.67,0:11:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家父在幕府末期時常說\N我打造的刀創造出新時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.51,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家父憑此信念製造出的刀\N奪走許多人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.95,0:11:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人怎麼是創造新時代\N我無法認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸  伊織！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.03,0:11:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且現在是明治\N和平時代終於降臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武士們放下刀劍\N所以我一樣也不做刀匠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定只做生活用具\N過和平的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 你和你父親相反\N擁護和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼主義的我是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.72,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡和平\N我想任何人都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天真 你太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼和平的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想顛覆這和平時代的人\N真真實實的還活在世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空 非常抱歉\N提出了無理的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣好嗎？緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.24,0:12:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是不殺人的逆刃刀\N卻也是打鬥的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在不忍心叫那樣的人來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.42,0:12:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重頭再來尋找逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位劍客…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是有什麼理由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不幫他打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就把父親留下的\N最後一把刀讓給它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.34,0:12:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣和平的明治\N已經不需要刀劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確定是拔刀齊  趕緊報告志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天真 太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的長像\N還有說話的樣子都很軟弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.72,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,施加壓力的話絕對行得通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.32,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空的和平生活\N我不能自私的去攪亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我說太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強叫他做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有刀匠的真心\N只會是件差勁的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法跟折斷逆刃刀的宗次郎\N或是志志雄打鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有形體的逆刃刀一無是處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.45,0:13:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的逆刃刀\N必須要超越斷掉的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.79,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼教出少根筋的女兒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正在京都的刀匠裏尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？認輸了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛苦無！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手 握手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.81,0:13:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空要是替我打造逆刃刀\N志志雄一定不會放過他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想把和平過日的一家人\N牽連進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵屋也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是以前御庭番眾的成員\N也不可能平安無事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到下個刀匠前\N必須離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治 交待你的事辦好了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預定要的火藥都買好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄\N你不是和宗次郎在一起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要他負責\N去把東日本的十本刀找來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.86,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們都像安慈那樣不好找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.09,0:14:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西日本這邊\N我直接吩咐下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.37,0:15:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀集結之後就開始國變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了吧！ 同志們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,群起暴動的時刻來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各自的準備先做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 志志雄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上去聯絡全國的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話還沒說完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀全部集合好\N要花不少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然大家都已經充滿了殺機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為慶祝國變\N先讓十本刀拿拔刀齊來血祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄 要三思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀\N是擔任重要任務的特攻部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.52,0:15:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿來對付拔刀齊 \N萬一傷到他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始我也嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題\N十本刀沒有那麼脆弱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 由美姐說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的十本刀\N不會輸給拔刀齊一個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說大話 獵刀張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在大阪住一陣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.67,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正想展露一下\N最近得到的愛刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.38,0:16:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這個臭劍客剛好可以殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.82,0:16:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經吸了好幾個人的血\N你們看這把刀耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是美的讓人目不轉睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.19,0:16:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是這樣\N一講到刀劍的事眼睛就亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治 拔刀齊有什麼動向？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒掌握他的行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.37,0:16:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只知道日前他和\N新井赤空的兒子青空接觸過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.18,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋求替代被宗次郎弄碎的\N那把逆刃刀吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空拒絕替他打造新刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.62,0:16:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空留下的最後一把刀\N並沒有交給拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末期的名刀匠\N新井赤空留下的最後一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正事當前你不要亂來壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管緋村和爺爺怎麼說\N不趕緊拿到新刀的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咕嚕咕嚕咕嚕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！掃把 掃把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掃把？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是說我的頭髮嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小孩真好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小朋友 你爸爸呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨 需要什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有赤空的最後一把刀嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家父的最後一把刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 偶然聽人談到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名刀匠新井赤空的最後一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不可以借看一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這人是從哪裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.32,0:18:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家父的刀現今全都下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我手邊一把也沒留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？大概是我聽錯了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡刀劍\N一心想要耍不同風格的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才會當上劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.01,0:18:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.73,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.24,0:18:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？這叫逆中空納刀\N沒幾個劍客會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過真的沒有最後的一把刀\N太震驚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.78,0:19:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,許許多多的刀裏面\N我最喜歡赤空的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太震驚了\N好像手又想揮第二次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.16,0:19:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣的工夫\N我從來不人前表演第二次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有眼福了\N好好看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏沒有家父的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.47,0:19:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一把刀已經奉為御神刀\N獻給白山神社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然真的有嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.75,0:19:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事不宜遲 我馬上去拜見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你們太壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在還不確定你說的\N是真還是假之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小孩借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在那裏別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會亂來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:20:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要是吵鬧的話\N小孩會變怎樣我不敢保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對那老哥再施點壓力\N拜託他一定要打造逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要告訴他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一把刀被稱做作御神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.75,0:20:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爸爸的刀裏面\N唯一沒有染上血腥的一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連那把都沾上血腥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.59,0:20:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸就不是真正的刀匠\N只不過製造殺人道具的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.73,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那個時候不說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.50,0:20:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸的名譽固然重要\N現在卻是伊織的命比較…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.37,0:20:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難道沒有看那男人的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是喜歡刀劍的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.31,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是喜歡拿刀殺人的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他拿到爸爸的刀之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.75,0:20:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不拿手邊的東西來試刀\N是不會善罷甘休的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.02,0:20:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.25,0:20:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不再打造刀劍了\N為什麼還會變成這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.89,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是剛剛那位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我詳細狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管那麼多快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你回京都來了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.67,0:21:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有急事要通知爺爺  準備一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從婆婆那兒來的信鴿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要傳達情報給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是小操傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青空的兒子\N被志志雄的人強帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.54,0:21:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的逆刃刀斷了不能用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.77,0:21:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了也不能盡力發揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不能去報仇的 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.85,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.82,0:22:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空的最後一把刀\N到底是怎樣的殺人刀呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不是來神社參拜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.98,0:22:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把小孩放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.95,0:22:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十字刀疤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你就是\N有名的殺人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是來拿赤空的\N最後一把刀嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.66,0:22:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放棄吧！誰敢來阻止我\N我就殺了他

